0) Prerequisites: McStas 2.4.1 installed with Perl tools

1) Mac and Linux:
   mcstas2vitess.pl ESS_butterfly.comp as_a_source
   (Can only happen on a Unix - tool looks broken on windows)

2) Windows:
   Transport .c code to Windows and perform
   gcc -lm -O2 McStas_ESS_butterfly.c -o mcstas_ess_butterfly.exe

3) Create docs using Linux or Macos mcdoc.pl:
mcdoc.pl .

